@startuml
title MicroMeet - Activity Diagram (Create Meetup)

start
:1. Host opens Create Meetup screen;
:2. Host enters meetup details (title, time, capacity, description);
:3. Host enters location details;
:4. Host clicks "Create";
:5. System validates inputs;

if (Inputs valid?) then (Yes)
  :6. System creates Meetup entity;
  :7. System saves meetup;
  :8. Show "Meetup created" confirmation;
else (No)
  :9. Show validation errors;
  :10. Host updates inputs;
endif

stop

legend bottom
Steps mapping (numbers match actions):
1 Open create meetup screen
2 Enter meetup details
3 Enter location details
4 Click Create
5 Validate inputs
6 Create meetup entity
7 Save meetup
8 Show confirmation
9 Show validation errors
10 Update inputs
endlegend

@enduml